    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLE HORDES OF MONSTERS</h2>Fight your way through hundreds of randomly constructed monsters all with interesting visuals and dangerous powers. Destroy these creatures, and the bosses that command them, to claim victory and increase your own power with new weapons, perks, and money. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/104d553ba378cc630158d298cf501e83.poster.avif?t=1759862096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/104d553ba378cc630158d298cf501e83.webm?t=1759862096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/104d553ba378cc630158d298cf501e83.mp4?t=1759862096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND POWERFUL WEAPONS</h2>Thousands of randomized weapons packed with exciting special abilities and statistics are locked away in treasure chests waiting for you to win them by defeating your foes. Collect weapons and create your own high-powered loadout to decimate your enemies. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/839528ab8578af11c32248901b24726d.poster.avif?t=1759862096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/839528ab8578af11c32248901b24726d.webm?t=1759862096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/839528ab8578af11c32248901b24726d.mp4?t=1759862096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT THROUGH UNIQUE LEVELS</h2>Use your hyper fast movement abilities to speed through levels and dominate the selection of specialized gamemodes. More than fifty different unique rooms await you, each with their own atmosphere and visual elements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/37b39bd6a3d4272362d08a9c7a29f4c4.poster.avif?t=1759862096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/37b39bd6a3d4272362d08a9c7a29f4c4.webm?t=1759862096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019110/extras/37b39bd6a3d4272362d08a9c7a29f4c4.mp4?t=1759862096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
